pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應承我 唔可以當手足係condom？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋揸住佢個春袋 呢粒核彈會令到中共好驚 手足就嚟贏 千祈唔可以中五毛分化撚嘅計 推走熱門行動Post 唔係我哋就嚟輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可 煲底見！"},{"pid":"de3958ff89998a481383a2d70428f4e413dddea4","tid":1975514,"uid":3522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 其實真係柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f0f63a3045e46296377b0d6f2f78d90bc20394","tid":1975514,"uid":29283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fab01b3fe9305e99d6f25c1943ea9b0bfd85dd5f","tid":1975514,"uid":230239,"like":70,"dislike":6,"score":64,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲簽聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"咪係"},{"pid":"55e06b30c5b89e14a14d20fde0fd6c1c2a23fc36","tid":1975514,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0084a4e7d15bfe98d88783a6b1e7713ad32370","tid":1975514,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB